overview: London Home Cleaner is a cleaning company that performs every cleaning task related to your home or office. Our services include one off cleaning, regular cleaning, end of tenancy cleaning, carpet and upholstery cleaning, etc. We have special training program for our workers so you can sure they know what they are doing and they will achieve the results that you expect, sometimes even better. Our company is a leader in the area of cleaning services in London and it’s not only because the quality of our services but also because of the prices we offer- they are unmatched. We keep lowest prices in order to make our services available to as many people as possible. For more information related to our company and our services you can give us a call and receive a free quote. Our staff works every day, including weekends and holidays so you can reach us in a comfortable for you time.
